  "summary": "Step-by-step procedure for releasing the API service to production, including rollback.",
  "summary_source": "author",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "prose",
      "format": "plain",
      "text": "Pre-flight checks",
      "level": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "prose",
      "format": "plain",
      "text": "Confirm staging is healthy and that the change-log entry has been merged before promoting an artefact to production."
    },
    {
      "type": "prose",
      "format": "markdown",
      "text": "1. Run the smoke suite against staging.\n1. Promote the artefact via the deploy CLI.\n1. Watch the canary dashboard for 10 minutes before scaling."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "text": "deploy promote --service api --from staging --to prod --canary 5"
    }
  ],
